--------------------------------------------------------------------
Remember to set environment varible:

  (csh/tcsh) 				(sh/bash)
  setenv XMODIFIERS @im=xcin		export XMODIFIERS='@im=xcin'
  setenv GTK_IM_MODULE xim		export GTK_IM_MODULE=xim

Finally, to start the GCIN input method daemon, use command:

  exec gcin &

